  {
    "hotel_id": "2727823",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/u-i-j-hotel-hostel/hotel/tainan-tw.html",
    "name": "U.I.J Hotel&Hostel (UIJ)",
    "detail": "It’s not my first time to visit Tainan, but it’s definitely the best stay I had so far and I would love to recommend to my friends!! UIJ is close to the Tainan art museum expo 2 and it only takes 20 mins to the popular spots by feet. It’s very chic, stylish and clean! The staffs always had a smile on their face and great attitude. Make us felt truly welcomed and pleased. We especially love the fragrance oil that mixed with wood science they used indoor, keep us claim and relax. The room was great, air conditioning was strong and easy to modify, the leather slippers were very comfy. Personal I adored the refillable still and sparking water (in glasses bottles) and 1 soft and 1 more supportive pillows the most. The soundproofing of our room was ok, since I had been wakes up by some noise from the hallway or next room in the morning around 6:00... but I think it’s more reflect to the guests behavior instead of the hotel itself. Also the shared area and balcony were all well designed that you can enjoy the time chatting with your friends like home or seize the chance taking nice photos like us ;) Oh did I mentioned their breakfast? If I remembered right I think they offered 6 types of breakfast with drink bar. Usually I will save my stomach for the classic Tainan food, but their breakfast were surprisingly good! We stayed 2 nights so we tried 4 of them and we were very happy with them all. My friend and I really enjoy our stay. It’s prefect choice for couples, group of friends and solo travelers! But personally I think it’s not very suitable for the people who travels with baby or children. Since they do have various decorations and detailed designs in the building, but kids are looking for playgrounds to run and seek. ",
